{"tid":2233072,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【中概股回歸】Bilibili傳聘4家投行為來港第二上市　擬集資最少78億（更新第二版）","createTime":"2020-10-07T00:43:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T01:07:34.000Z","uid":10199,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"dc4dc469f84b0f865ed8f205e3d06679c8c0d3af","tid":2233072,"uid":10199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T00:43:25.000Z","msg":"路透報道，騰訊 （00700） 及阿里巴巴 （09988） 持股的視頻網站嗶哩嗶哩（Bilibili， 美：BILI，俗稱B站）已委任4間投行，分別為大摩、摩通、高盛和瑞銀，為其安排來港第二上市，目標明年上市，集資最少10億美元（約78億港元）。對此，嗶哩嗶哩不予置評。<br />\n<br />\n嗶哩嗶哩昨晚美股大漲7.89%，收報45.1美元，最新市值高達155.8億美元（約1207億港元）。嗶哩嗶哩股價今年已累升142%。而在最新回流消息刺激下，嗶哩嗶哩今日（6日）在美交易時段再上升，截至本港時間晚上約10時45分，報47.48美元，漲5.3%。<br />\n<br />\n中美關係惡化，在美上市的中國企業回歸中港上市，截至目前，已有網易 （09999） 、京東 （09618） 、百勝中國 （09987） 、華住集團 （01179） 、寶尊 （09991） ，年底陸續有更多中國企業回巢"},{"pid":"d6197a3a65400a53c33c6d8fb0223d19f086d6a2","tid":2233072,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T00:57:37.000Z","msg":"咁係美國上左市 集左既資會點？"},{"pid":"5f0c1d0eb0897b56889ce2823bf2550f5765daa8","tid":2233072,"uid":24306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T01:06:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幾時到91porn上市<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8f701de8a2db703d0f9232fa753b5f7fe5d1d38","tid":2233072,"uid":263183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6197a3a65400a53c33c6d8fb0223d19f086d6a2","tid":2233072,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T00:57:37.000Z","msg":"咁係美國上左市 集左既資會點？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T01:06:39.000Z","msg":"照舊 好似係"},{"pid":"8c5629375a1c712e468726e120a34042894b6654","tid":2233072,"uid":278414,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T01:07:34.000Z","msg":"支那不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji